<div type="abstract"><head>Vermerk über Ausstellung eines Kredenzbriefs</head><p>Kredenzbrief für Heinrich Huber an Hersbruck wegen der Zollforderungen an Nürnberger.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_115" id="57v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_115_r2l10"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> ein credecʒ an ~ dıe von Herſpruk . auf den <expan>Hubn<ex>er</ex></expan> . als von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_115_r2l11">ʒölle <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> da mıt dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey Jn beſwert <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . als ſıe vns fürbracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_115_r2l12"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>act<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_115" id="57v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> ein credecz an die von Herspruk auf den
                                <expan>Hubn<ex>er</ex></expan> als von
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> zölle <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> da
                        mit die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey in beswert
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> als sie uns fürbracht
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
